This paper is about interpreting NLP models, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and machine learning (cs.LG) in NLP models, as well as the use of visualization techniques (cs.CV) to aid in interpretation. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of adversarial attacks (cs.AI) as an interpretation method.
